com.novell.ldapchai.exception
Enum ChaiError

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<ChaiError>
      com.novell.ldapchai.exception.ChaiError
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ChaiError>
public enum ChaiError
extends Enum<ChaiError>

An enumerarion of error codes known to the LDAP Chai API. When a ChaiException is thrown, it will be issued with one of the values of this enumeration.

Author:
Jason D. Rivard
